OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ftending to ease through the evening
OL,7,Fand overnight, with clear spells for
OL,8,Fmany. Turning chilly, and under the
OL,9,Fclearest skies a touch of frost is
OL,10,Fpossible in the north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FDrier and brighter for many,
OL,13,Fwith spells of sunshine. A few showers
OL,14,Fremain possible, perhaps heavy in the
OL,15,Fsouth. Still a chilly northerly breeze
OL,16,Fmeans temperatures will remain below
OL,17,Faverage.
